    "The transformer fine-tuning is a more challenging task characterized by complex data dependencies.",
    "Further, existing works do not consider communication traffic while integrating manycore architecture.",
    "The NoC framework integrating the computing cores necessitates optimization to facilitate efficient data exchange and support compute parallelism.",
    "In this paper, we fill this gap in the state-of-the-art by proposing a heterogeneous multi-core 3D architecture aimed at enabling transformer models to run efficiently for both fine-tuning and inference on the edge.",
    "Table I summarizes and compares a few of the existing notable transformer accelerators from industry and academia with respect to our proposed Atleus architecture."
